UID:8526-1776371400-1776380400@jazzbistro.ca
SUMMARY:From Japan/MTL: M.A.K. Trio (Night 1 of 2)
DESCRIPTION:Montreal-based musicians Adrian Vedady (bass) and Kate Wyatt (piano) unite with Masashi Usui (saxophones) from Japan for a concert tour in Japan and Canada. The M.A.K. trio (Masashi\, Adrian\, Kate) promises a musical journey with a selection of exquisite standards and original compositions\, showcasing the group’s devotion to sonic elegance\, textural richness\, and emotional intensity\, rather than technical bravado\, showiness\, or excessive intellectualization. \n \nCOVER: $20
URL:https://jazzbistro.ca/event/from-japan-mtl-m-a-k-trio-night-1-of-2/
END:VEVENT
